INSERT INTO `mysys_module_engage` VALUES (1,'人才招聘','2013-08-16','<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px;\">&nbsp;浙商银行是经中国银监会批准设立的第十二家全国性股份制商业银行，总行设在杭州，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2004年8月18日正式开业。目前已在北京、天津、上海、南京、济南、深圳、成都、西安、兰州和浙江省内的所有省辖市和主要县（市）设立（筹建）了60余家分支机构。</span></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">浙商银行兰州分行位于兰州市白银路<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">308号，是浙商银行总行直属分行，2009 年12月获准筹建， 2010年11月19日开始对外试营业。兰州分行秉承浙商银行&ldquo;一体两翼&rdquo;的市场和业务定位，以公司业务为主体，小企业银行和投资银行业务为两翼，结合甘肃地方经济金融形势，顺势而为、勇于创新，致力于促进甘肃及周边地区经济建设，让每个客户从浙商银行的金融服务中得到更多价值。</span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">现因分行业务发展和人才储备需要，面向社会诚聘金融人才，欢迎立志于创业发展的有志、有识之士加盟浙商银行。我行将为每位加盟的员工构建良好的职业生涯发展之路，并提供业内具有竞争力的薪酬福利待遇。</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">&nbsp;一、基本条件</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">1、负责、诚信；<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n2、沟通、合作良好；&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n3、从业记录和社会信用良好；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n4、原则上大学本科及以上学历；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n5、应聘部门负责人的年龄原则上在40周岁左右，其他员工的年龄原则上在35周岁左右；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n6、身体素质良好；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n7、具有岗位所要求的专业知识、从业经历和业务能力。</span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">二、招聘岗位、人数及职位要求</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 12.727272033691406px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-indent: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 254, 254); margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"600\" summary=\"\" border=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 625px;\">\r\n    <tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"104\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">部门</strong></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">岗位</strong></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">人数</strong></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"387\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">职位要求</strong></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"104\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">业务管理部</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">负责人</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">1名</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"387\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、&nbsp;</span>精通公司授信业务、产品及营销方案设计；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、&nbsp;</span>具有丰富的公司业务营销管理经验和业务开拓能力；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、&nbsp;</span>熟悉零售银行、电子银行业务及相关产品；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4、&nbsp;</span>具有较强的市场开拓能力、营销组织能力和沟通协调能力；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5、&nbsp;</span>具有<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">8年以上商业银行从业经历，3年以上相关岗位管理经验。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">6、&nbsp;</span>熟悉本地市场情况，有一定客户资源者优先。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">公司业务管理岗</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">1名</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"387\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、&nbsp;</span>有客户经理绩效管理经验，熟悉公司业务培训、考核；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、&nbsp;</span>具有<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3年以上分行公司业务管理经验；</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、&nbsp;</span>熟悉兰州当地市场，有一定客户资源者优先。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"104\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">风险管理部</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">授信审查岗</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">1名</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"387\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、&nbsp;</span>熟悉授信、风险和放款等信贷管理业务，熟悉当地市场情况；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、&nbsp;</span>对授信客户的经营与财务状况具有较强的风险识别、防控能力；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、&nbsp;</span>具有较强的综合分析、文字表达能力；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4、&nbsp;</span>具有<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5年以上商业银行从业经验，具有3年以上商业银行授信审查或风险管理、合规从业经历。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">合规管理岗</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">2名</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"387\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、&nbsp;</span>从事相关专业<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3年以上，精通法律、法规、银行业监管规定，熟悉授信等银行业务管理；</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、&nbsp;</span>具有较强的合规风险识别、分析和判断能力；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、&nbsp;</span>具有法律专业或司法职业资格考试者优先。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"104\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">会计科技部</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">负责人</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">1名</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"387\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、&nbsp;</span>具备扎实的会计管理专业知识和技能，具有会计条线管理经验；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、&nbsp;</span>熟练掌握相关业务流程及规定，熟悉流程化会计业务运作；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、&nbsp;</span>具有较强组织管理、沟通协调能力；</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4、&nbsp;</span>8年以上商业银行从业经验，<span style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3年以上相关岗位管理经验。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"104\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">计划财务部</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"95\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: 13px; margin: 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 590px;\">财务管理岗</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"57\" style=\"font